{"about_the_game":"You who used to work as a developer in a city. The longing for your hometown has grown so great that you come back to your hometown.<br>When you opened your eyes to the mysterious light of the shrine, you realized that 575 years ago you came back.<br>How do you survive in this poor town?<br><br>Sage Mountain is an oriental fantasy farming game.<br>You will spend most of your time farming, fishing and cooking after a time travel to the past.<br>You will also have relationships with the village people.<br>Find the monsters hidden all over!<br><br>Feature<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make up the farm! Learn how the villagers live and mingle. Plant crops, fruits.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Try fishing, too. If you want to have time to think alone, catch fish!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find the monsters hiding everywhere and get your hands on them!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Take the risk of finding mate/rials and make special items.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>I'm a Chef! Try to grow and process the crops you need to cook!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get wood, stone, ore to make furniture and items!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1591431623","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062850/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1591431623","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062850/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1591431623","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062850/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1591431623","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam